summary: This document is a calendar entry for a meeting titled 'Epstein FOIA Next Steps - Noel Team' scheduled for April 14, 2021, involving personnel from the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS). It indicates planning for next steps regarding Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) requests related to the Epstein case.

events.title: Epstein FOIA Next Steps Meeting
